commit.message:
sources.am, [...]: Rebuilt.

	* sources.am, Makefile.in: Rebuilt.
	* scripts/makemake.tcl: Accept -verbose command-line option.
	(is_verbose): New global.
	(verbose): Use it.
	(classify_source_file): Don't special case '.' for 'package'
	type.

From-SVN: r114051
